<author>nʿym ʿạṭf</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lk yạ sydy yạ frḥty yạ bsmty ạ̉qdm tsbyḥty
 wkl ṭyr fy ạlsmạ wkl ʿsẖb qd nmạ
 wạlzhr fy ạ̉gẖṣạnh lk ygẖny bạsmạ
 2- lk yạ sydy mḥbty wtẖqty yạ ḍạmnaⁿạ slạmty
 ffy ṭryq gẖrbty ʿynạk tḥmy kẖṭwty
 wạ̹n ḍllt tạỷhaⁿạ tʿyd ly bṣyrty
 3- lk yạ sydy lk ạ̉nạ bjmlty yạ mljạ̉y wrạḥty
 ạ̉ʿṭyk ậmạly ạlkbạr ạ̉ʿṭyk lyly wạlnhạr
 ạ̉ʿṭyk qlby kẖạlṣaⁿạ qdsh fy nwr wnạr</lyrics>
<title>lk yạ sydy</title>
</song>